>舉辦的冬奧<br />\n<br />\n南京政府年代翻譯?"},{"pid":"4872f0eae65d49050b271e8edb7a65a0167f7d8b","tid":1929802,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"取消啦，爆到七彩仲搞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8b96512251e34c646a66aaa93a66daba1f6bb9","tid":1929802,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b7389790343bbc4cb65671bdd7b5373d0f83414b","tid":1929802,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"同年的冬天則緊接由中國<span style=\"color: red;\">北平</span>舉辦的冬奧<br />\n<br />\n南京政府年代翻譯?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個位好笑"},{"pid":"bb0cfd5fed87d0f31516e22a1e0794bfe7c0fb5e","tid":1929802,"uid":205616,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b7389790343bbc4cb65671bdd7b5373d0f83414b","tid":1929802,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"同年的冬天則緊接由中國<span style=\"color: red;\">北平</span>舉辦的冬奧<br />\n<br />\n南京政府年代翻譯?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"主觀個人翻譯<br />\n我個人唔承認中華人民共和國政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e0d9f1ada845e0e7d852169f6191cdb4edf873","tid":1929802,"uid":161440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a61f7ee420963ad3f23800e6f5472d9f974975d","tid":1929802,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"李慧詩等唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g